block.p: JENNINGS-Edward. On January 17, 1998, of Long Boat Key, FL, formerly of Mamaroneck, NY. Beloved husband of the late Molly Jennings. Loving brother of John, Thomas, Patrick, Mary, Bridget, Angela, and the late Tobias. Also survived by several nieces and nephews. The family will receive friends Monday, 2-4, 7-9 PM at the William H. Graham Funeral Home, 1036 Boston Post Rd., Rye, NY. Mass of Christian Burial Tuesday, 10 AM, at the Church of the Resurrection, Rye, NY. Interment to follow at Long Island National Cemetery, Pinelawn, NY. In lieu of flowers, contributions may be made to the Lung Cancer Service, Memorial Sloan-Kettering, 1275 York Ave., New York, NY.
